etready.com/wp-content/uploads/bandag-2.jpg" alt="bandag-2" width="810" height="267" /></a></p>\n<p>After stumbing with <a href="http://wpgetready.com/2015/02/eating-your-own-dog-food-nextcellent-1-9-25-1-fixes/" target="_blank">several issues</a>,  a <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/nextcellent-gallery-nextgen-legacy/" target="_blank">second round of fixes is launched</a>.</p>\n<p>I took special care on this round. We are making more and more complex decisions and diversifying our development. One <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/topic/nextcellent-beta" target="_blank">beta there</a>, a <a href="https://bitbucket.org/wpgetready/nextcellent/branch/1.9.25.2" target="_blank">branch here</a>, (didn&#8217;t I mention I also have few other branches open locally? ) , and if everything goes right, we&#8217;ll end up merging everything into Nextcellent. In more than one way, we are working better now than before.</p>\n<p>We are currently working towards to 1.9.26 version. I&#8217;m focusing in to stabilize the code and improve some parts. We also have high expectations about what is coming to Nextcellent.</p>\n<p>Take care and have a wonderful day. You deserve it.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=''yarpp-related-rss''>\n<p>Related posts:<ol>\n<li><a href="http://wpgetready.com/2014/06/day-0061-nextcellent-1-9-20/" rel="bookmark" title="Day 0061 &#8211; Nextcellent 1.9.20">Day 0061 &#8211; Nextcellent 1.9.20 </a> <small>Nextcellent 1.9.20 fixes few issues, bringing nggtag back to life....</small></li>\n<li><a href="http://wpgetready.com/2014/09/nextcellent-1-9-21-just-launched-here-are-the-news/" rel="bookmark" title="Nextcellent 1.9.21 just launched. Here are the news">Nextcellent 1.9.21 just launched. Here are the news </a> <small>Hi everybody. Nextcellent is rolling out 1.9.21 and it&#8217;s celebrating...</small></li>\n<li><a href="http://wpgetready.com/2015/01/nextcellent-19-25-is-coming/" rel="bookmark" title="Nextcellent 1.9.25 is coming&#8230